## Brand Functional Palette Field

A field that captures a brand functional color palette (used by the brand-guide system)

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import BrandFunctionalPaletteField from 'https://cardstack.com/base/brand-functional-palette';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field palette = contains(BrandFunctionalPaletteField);
}
```
